text: Mónica Torres is a Mexican taekwondo practitioner. She won a silver medal in finweight at the 1987 World Taekwondo Championships in Barcelona, after being defeated by Jang Eu-suk in the final. She won a silver medal in finweight at the 1989 World Taekwondo Championships, after being defeated by Chin Yu-fang in the final.
